#: includes/class-bol-admin-page.php:358
msgid "Overview"
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-bol-admin-page.php:359
msgid "Big Orange Pardot adds a Gutenberg block that embeds a Pardot (Account Engagement) form directly on any page or post. Rather than using an iframe, it renders a native HTML form that submits directly to your Pardot form handler, giving you full control over styling and layout."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-bol-admin-page.php:360
msgid "The plugin also automatically captures marketing attribution data (UTM parameters, Google Click ID, landing page URL, and referrer) into cookies on every page load, then injects those values as hidden fields on any Pardot form found on the page — even forms loaded dynamically after the page renders."
msgstr ""

